# Design Recommendations for MMS-MFC

**Based on:** Competitive UX analysis of Railnova, SignatureRail, Tracsis
**Purpose:** Actionable changes to improve MMS-MFC design
**Target:** Designers and developers

---

## Executive Summary

### Top 5 Quick Wins

| # | Change | Evidence | Effort | Impact |
|---|--------|----------|--------|--------|
| 1 | Add status color palette consistency | Railnova uses green/yellow/red everywhere | Low | High |
| 2 | Make status badges clickable filters | Railnova dashboard flow | Medium | High |
| 3 | Add slide-out detail panels | Railnova avoids full page navigation | Medium | High |
| 4 | Add hover tooltips to Gantt bars | Railnova prevents information overload | Low | Medium |
| 5 | Improve navigation active state | Railnova sidebar has clear indication | Low | Medium |

