## 1. Status Color System

### Current Problem
MMS-MFC lacks consistent status color palette across components.

### Recommendation
Adopt Railnova's color system throughout all components:

```css
/* Status Colors - Add to globals.css */
:root {
  --status-operational: #15B371;
  --status-degraded: #F5A623;
  --status-restricted: #E53E3E;
  --status-maintenance: #6B7280;
  --status-unknown: #A0AEC0;
}

/* Blueprint.js integration */
.bp5-tag.status-operational { background-color: var(--status-operational); }
.bp5-tag.status-degraded { background-color: var(--status-degraded); }
.bp5-tag.status-restricted { background-color: var(--status-restricted); }
.bp5-tag.status-maintenance { background-color: var(--status-maintenance); }
```

### Where to Apply
- Dashboard KPI cards
- Fleet list status column
- Map markers
- Gantt chart bars
- Allocation panel status

