## 2. Interactive Status Badges

### Current Problem
Status badges are display-only. Users must manually filter.

### Recommendation
Make status counts/badges clickable to filter the view:

```typescript
// Example: DashboardKPIs.tsx
<Tag
  intent={Intent.SUCCESS}
  onClick={() => setFilter({ status: 'operational' })}
  interactive
>
  {operationalCount} Operational
</Tag>
```

### User Flow Improvement
```
Before: Dashboard → Menu → Fleet → Filter dropdown → Select status → Apply
After:  Dashboard → Click "12 Restricted" → Filtered view
```

