## 3. Slide-Out Detail Panels

### Current Problem
Clicking an item navigates to a new page, losing context.

### Recommendation
Use Blueprint.js Drawer for detail views:

```typescript
// Example usage
<Drawer
  isOpen={selectedAsset !== null}
  onClose={() => setSelectedAsset(null)}
  size="400px"
  position="right"
  title={selectedAsset?.name}
>
  <AssetDetailContent asset={selectedAsset} />
</Drawer>
```

### Benefits
- User maintains context of the list
- Quick comparison between items
- Faster navigation flow

