## 6. Map Component Improvements

### Current Problem
Map markers lack status coloring.

### Recommendation
Color markers based on asset status:

```typescript
// Marker color based on status
const getMarkerColor = (status: AssetStatus): string => {
  switch (status) {
    case 'operational': return '#15B371';
    case 'degraded': return '#F5A623';
    case 'restricted': return '#E53E3E';
    case 'maintenance': return '#6B7280';
    default: return '#A0AEC0';
  }
};

// Apply to Leaflet markers
L.circleMarker(position, {
  color: getMarkerColor(asset.status),
  fillColor: getMarkerColor(asset.status),
  fillOpacity: 0.8,
  radius: 8
});
```

