## 7. Filter Bar Pattern

### Current Problem
Filtering is inconsistent across pages.

### Recommendation
Add consistent filter bar pattern:

```typescript
// Reusable FilterBar component
<FilterBar>
  <Select
    items={assetTypes}
    placeholder="Asset type"
    onItemSelect={setTypeFilter}
  />
  <MultiSelect
    items={statuses}
    placeholder="Status"
    selectedItems={statusFilter}
    onItemSelect={addStatusFilter}
  />
  <DateRangeInput
    value={dateRange}
    onChange={setDateRange}
  />
  <Button text="Reset" onClick={resetFilters} minimal />
</FilterBar>

// Show active filters as chips
<div className="active-filters">
  {activeFilters.map(filter => (
    <Tag onRemove={() => removeFilter(filter)}>
      {filter.label}
    </Tag>
  ))}
</div>
```

