## Anti-Patterns to Avoid

### From SignatureRail Analysis

| Anti-Pattern | Why It's Bad | Alternative |
|--------------|--------------|-------------|
| Cryptic abbreviations (DOW, Cxpts) | Requires training, causes errors | Full labels with tooltips |
| 15+ columns visible | Cognitive overload | Progressive disclosure |
| Spreadsheet aesthetic | Feels dated, low usability | Card-based layout |
| Desktop-only UI | Deployment friction | Responsive web app |
| Modal windows | Loses context | Slide-out panels |

